<h2 id="2-矩阵分解"><a href="#2-矩阵分解" class="headerlink" title="2. 矩阵分解"></a>2. 矩阵分解</h2><p><img src="/images/recommendation/rs-six-month-06.png" alt="Latent semantic model"></p>
