<h2 id="1-Vocabulary"><a href="#1-Vocabulary" class="headerlink" title="1. Vocabulary"></a>1. Vocabulary</h2><ul>
<li>unconscious</li>
</ul>
<p><img src="/images/english/ef-l6u2l4.png" alt=""></p>
<table>
