      <title><![CDATA[深入浅出 Entropy Based]]></title>
      <url>http://iequa.com/2016/09/12/ml-entropy-base/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<script type="text/x-mathjax-config">
  MathJax.Hub.Config({
    extensions: ["tex2jax.js"],
    jax: ["input/TeX"],
    tex2jax: {
      inlineMath: [ ['$','$'], ['\\(','\\)'] ],
