      <title><![CDATA[CART (not finish)]]></title>
      <url>http://iequa.com/2016/08/24/ml-CART/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<script type="text/x-mathjax-config">
  MathJax.Hub.Config({
    extensions: ["tex2jax.js"],
    jax: ["input/TeX"],
    tex2jax: {
      inlineMath: [ ['$','$'], ['\\(','\\)'] ],
